cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SD

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the emergence of compositional languages in multi-agent communication systems. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses deep learning techniques to facilitate the emergence of compositional languages. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep neural network agents for the experiments. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper explores the emergence of languages through iterated learning in populations of neural agents. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with language and communication.
